                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-06-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 21, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay states that this Government is opposed to raising the revenue above 5
                    per cent effective, but directs Mr. Rockhill to refrain from opposing
                    proposition of eventual discussion if it will aid in bringing negotiations to a
                    close.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
